  [∀ i, NormedSpace 𝕜 (E i)] [∀ i, NormedAddCommGroup (E₁ i)] [∀ i, NormedSpace 𝕜 (E₁ i)]
  [∀ i, NormedAddCommGroup (E' i)] [∀ i, NormedSpace 𝕜 (E' i)] [∀ i, NormedAddCommGroup (Ei i)]
